item.title: CVE-2022-39157|2024-08-03T11:10:32.613Z -- siemens -- parasolid%20v34.0
item.description: A vulnerability has been identified in Parasolid V34.0 (All versions < V34.0.252), Parasolid V34.0 (All versions >= V34.0.252 < V34.0.254), Parasolid V34.1 (All versions < V34.1.242), Parasolid V34.1 (All versions >= V34.1.242 < V34.1.244), Parasolid V35.0 (All versions < V35.0.170), Parasolid V35.0 (All versions >= V35.0.170 < V35.0.184), Simcenter Femap (All versions < V2023.1). The affected application contains an out of bounds read past the end of an allocated structure while parsing specially crafted X_T files. This could allow an attacker to execute code in the context of the current process. (ZDI-CAN-17745)

item.title: CVE-2022-43397|2024-08-03T13:32:57.387Z -- siemens -- parasolid%20v34.0
